  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">William Lloyd Garrison says that his son, Charles Follen Garrison, died last night at age seven after a severe illness lasting a week. The Garrisons ask Theodore Parker to participate in the funeral services tomorrow. Mrs. Parker is also invited.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
